Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/zloncar/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    
    or in one go: git submodule update --init
    
To add new plugin

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule add http://github.com/usename/repo bundle/repo
